Looking at the past, Grindel feels betrayed.
"Unfortunately, there have been people who have noticed this mistake and pierced the press instead of addressing me about it," Grindel said of the acceptance of an expensive watch that led to his resignation in April 2019.
"Personally, I was very preoccupied with that.".
